      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation at a great value. It\u2019s a practical ride that still has plenty of life left to give!",
