    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The engine currently struggles to start and has a noticeable knock, while the transmission exhibits slipping between gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents on the passenger side, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would best serve as a dedicated project car or a source for spare parts for someone with the right tools and time.",
