    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are honored to present this superlative example, maintained to an uncompromising standard of excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory-fresh integrity. Every mechanical component has been meticulously vetted to ensure it operates with the precision and refinement expected of a premier-tier automobile. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of investment-grade quality, suited for the most discerning of collectors. Full documentation and service history are available for review.",
      "price": 48750.0,
